				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{R}{\mathrm{I}}_{\mathrm{S}}=\frac{{\mathrm{RFC}}_{S\left(\max \right)}+\kern0.5em {\mathrm{RNU}}_{S\left(\max \right)}}{2} $$\end{document}RIS=RFCSmax+RNUSmax2

The cultural importance index (CI) is defined by the following formula:
\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
