				\begin{document}$$ {\mathrm{CI}}_s=\sum \limits_{u={u}_1}^{u_{\mathrm{NC}}}\sum \limits_{i={i}_1}^{u_{\mathrm{NC}}}\raisebox{1ex}{${\mathrm{UR}}_{ui}$}\!\left/ \!\raisebox{-1ex}{$N$}\right. $$\end{document}CIs=∑u=u1uNC∑i=i1uNCURuiN

The cultural value (or importance value) of species in a given culture and the comparative importance of species inter culturally are receiving growing attention in ethnobotanical studies [26, 31]. This index is calculated using the following formula [32]:
\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ {\mathrm{CV}}_S=\left[\frac{N\kern0.5em {U}_S}{\begin{array}{cc}N& C\end{array}}\right]\times \left[\frac{\begin{array}{cc}F& {C}_S\end{array}}{N}\right]\times \left[\sum \limits_{\mu =\mu 1}^{\mu_{\mathrm{NC}}}\sum \limits_{\iota =\iota 1}^{\iota_N}\frac{{\mathrm{UR}}_{\mu \iota}}{N}\right] $$\end{document}CVS=NUSNC×FCSN×∑μ=μ1μNC∑ι=ι1ιNURμιN
